tion-of-chinese-character\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Help: Decomposition of Chinese character\"></a>:</b><br></p>\n          <p><b>Simplification rule <a target=\"_blank\"></a>:</b></p>\n          <p class=\"pre-inline\"><b>Simplification rule explained <a target=\"_blank\"></a>:</b><br></p>\n          <p><b>Variant rule :</b></p>\n          <p class=\"pre-inline\"><b>Variant rule clarification <a target=\"_blank\"></a>:</b><br></p>\n          <p><b>Applied rules <a target=\"_blank\"></a>:</b></p>\n          <p><b>New font rule <a target=\"_blank\"></a>:</b></p><a target=\"_blank\"><span></span></a>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"p-1 bg-primary col-md-9 col-sm-8 etymology-result\" id=\"etymologyCharacters\">\n        <h3><span></span></h3>\n        <p>There is no known oracle characters found. 没.</p>\n        <hr>\n        <h3><span></span></h3>\n        <p>There is no known bronze characters found. 没.</p>\n        <hr>\n        <h3><span></span> Seal characters (1)</h3>\n        <ul class=\"list-inline list-unstyled\">\n          <li class=\"text-center\"><img src=\"hanziyan-S06782.png\"></li>\n        </ul>\n        <hr>\n        <h3><span></span></h3>\n        <p></p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"two_children__horiz_even\">\n  <div id=\"yw11\">\n    <h4><span>砥</span>字的基本解释</h4>\n    <div>\n      <p>砥<br>dǐ<br>〔砥柱中流〕像砥柱山（在中国三门峡）那样屹立在黄河激流中，喻中坚人物或力量所起的支柱作用。<br>细的磨刀石：砥石。砥砺。<br><br></p>\n    </div>\n    <div><span>砥</span>字的汉语字典释义</div>\n    <div>\n      <p>[①]［dǐ］［zhǐ］<br>［《廣韻》職雉切，上旨，章。］<br>［《廣韻》諸氏切，上紙，章。］<br>［《廣韻》旨夷切，平脂，章。］<br>［《集韻》典禮切，上薺，端。］<br>(1)质地较细的磨刀石。<br>(2)磨。<br>(3)磨练；修养。参见“砥節”、“砥礪”。<br>(4)平均。<br>(5)平直；平坦。引申为公平。参见“砥平”、“砥直”。<br>(6)平安；安定。参见“砥平”、“砥屬”。<br>(7)阻挡；阻滞。</p>\n    </div>\n    <div><span>砥</span>字的康熙字典解释</div>\n    <div>\n      <p>【午集下】【石字部】　砥； 康熙笔画：10； 页码：<a href=\"https://images.yw11.com/kangxi/0828.gif\" target=\"_blank\"><span>页828第37</span></a><br>【廣韻】【韻會】【正韻】諸氏切【集韻】掌氏切，?音紙。磨石也。【書·禹貢】荆州礪砥砮丹。【註】砥細於礪。【山海經】崦嵫之山，其中多砥礪。　又平也，均也。【詩·小雅】周道如砥。　又借言節操。【禮·儒行】砥礪廉隅。　又砥砨，玉石。【史記·范睢傳】周有砥砨。　【說文】本作厎。或作底。【書·禹貢】厎柱析城。【註】厎柱，山名。在河水中。【前漢·梅福傳】爵祿束帛，天下之底石。　又【集韻】曲禮切，音邸。義同。</p>\n    </div>\n    <div><span>砥</span>字的源字形</div>\n    <div>\n      <h3>字源演变：</h3><span><span><img src=\"yw11-zixing-7825.gif\">小篆</span><span><img src=\"yw11-zixing-7825.gif\">楷体</span></span>\n      <h3>字形对比：</h3><span><span><img src=\"yw11-zixing-7825.gif\">中国大陆宋体</span><span><img src=\"yw11-zixing-7825.gif\">台湾细明体</span><span><img src=\"yw11-zixing-7825.gif\">香港明体</span><span><img src=\"yw11-zixing-7825.gif\">日本明朝体</span><span><img src=\"yw11-zixing-7825.gif\">韩国明朝体</span><span><img src=\"yw11-zixing-7825.gif\">旧字形</span></span>\n    </div>\n    <div><span>砥</span>字的起名意思</div>\n    <div>\n      <p>本义指质地很细的磨刀石，后引申为磨炼，勉励。</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <div id=\"yw11_en_transl\">whetstone<br>Basic explanation of words<br>whetstone<br>dǐ<br>[Mainstay in the middle of the stream] Standing like a mainstay mountain (in Sanmenxia, China) in the rapids of the Yellow River, it is a metaphor for the pillar role played by the backbone of the people or power.<br>Fine whetstone: the whetstone. Hardened.<br>whetstone<br>Chinese dictionary definition of words<br>[①] [dǐ] [zhǐ]<br>[\"Guangyun\" job pheasant cut, decree, chapter. ]<br>[\"Guang Yun\" cut by all the clan, put on paper, chapter. ]<br>[\"Guangyun\" aims to cut, level fat, and chapter. ]<br>[\"Ji Yun\" ceremony cut, top and end. ]<br>(1) A whetstone with a finer texture.<br>(2) Grinding.<br>(3) Training; self-cultivation. See also \"Tianjie\", \"Strengthening\".<br>(4) Average.<br>(5) Straight; flat. The extension is fair. See \"To Ping\", \"To Straight\".<br>(6) Safe and stable. See \"Tiping\", \"Tiping\".<br>(7) Block; block.<br>whetstone<br>Kangxi dictionary interpretation of words<br>[Afternoon Set 2] [Stone Character Department] 　砥; Kangxi Strokes: 10; Page Number: Page 828 Page 37<br>[Guang Yun] [Rhyme Meeting] [Zheng Yun] Zhu Shi cut [Ji Yun] Zhang Shi cut, on paper. The millstone also. 【Book·Yugong】Jingzhou Lihuo Dan. [Note] To be finer than grind. [Mountain and Sea Classic] The mountains of 崦嵫, many of them are tough.　It's flat, it's all. 【Poetry·Xiaoya】Thoughtful and thoughtful.　I borrowed words and morals. 【Rite·Confucianism】Strengthen Lian Yu.　Yu Yan, jade. [Historical Records · Fan Sui Biography] Zhou Youzhen.　【Said the text】This is the work. Or make the bottom. 【Book·Yugong】Analysis of the City of Sizhu. [Note] Sizhu, the name of the mountain. In the river water. [Previous Han·Meifu Biography] Juelu Shubo, the bottom stone of the world.　[Jiyun] Qu Liqie, Sound Mansion. The same meaning.<br>whetstone<br>Source glyph<br>Character evolution: Xiaozhuan<br>Italics<br>Font comparison: Song Ti, Mainland China<br>Taiwan Minutes<br>Hong Kong Mingti<br>Japanese Ming Dynasty<br>Korean Ming Dynasty<br>Old glyph<br>whetstone<br>Name meaning<br>The original meaning refers to a whetstone with a very fine texture, which is later extended to temper and encourage.</div>\n</div>\n<div></div>\n<hr>\n<div id=\"bkrs_pinyin\">dǐ, zhǐ</div>\n<div id=\"bkrs_transl\">\n  <div><strong>I</strong><i> сущ.</i></div>\n  <div>1) точило, оселок, точильный камень</div>\n  <div><span class=\"example-item\">剑待砥而后利 мечу необходимо точило, после которого он только и может стать острым</span></div>\n  <div><span class=\"example-item\">如砥 как точильный камень (равный, одинаковый)</span></div>\n  <div>2) чёрный (тёмный) самоцвет</div>\n  <div><span class=\"example-item\">白水宜玉, 黑水宜砥 в реке Байшуй (Белой) должна быть яшма, в реке Хэйшуй (Чёрной) ― тёмные самоцветы</span></div>\n  <div><strong>II</strong><i> гл.</i></div>\n  <div>1) точить; шлифовать, полировать</div>\n  <div>2)<i> перен.</i> совершенствовать, отделывать</div>\n  <div><span class=\"example-item\">文王砥德修政 Вэнь-ван совершенствовал принципы морали и улучшал дело управления</span></div>\n  <div>3) уравнивать; сравнивать; уравновешивать</div>\n  <div><span class=\"example-item\">砥其远迩 уравнивать их (земельные наделы), в зависимости от расстояния (удалённости участка)</span></div>\n  <div><strong>III</strong><i> прил./наречие</i></div>\n  <div>ровный</div>\n  <div><span class=\"example-item\">砥行 ровная дорога, ровный путь</span></div>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.mdbg.net/chinese/dictionary?page=worddict&wdrst=0&wdqtm=0&wdqcham=1&wdqt=\">MDBG</a> | <a href=\"https://bkrs.info/slovo.php?ch=砥\">BKRS</a> | <a href=\"https://dictionary.writtenchinese.com/#sk=砥&svt=pinyin\">WriCh</a> | <a href=\"http://www.qianyix.com/words/index.php?q=砥\">Qianyix</a> | <a href=\"https://www.yellowbridge.com/chinese/sentsearch.php?word=砥\">YBridge</a> | <a href=\"http://cca.xingtanlu.cn/?action=page&pid=8&do=search&name=砥\">Collocs</a> | <a href=\"https://characterpop.com/explode/砥\">ChPop</a> | <a href=\"https://visualchinesesearch.com/?query=砥\">SimCh</a> | <a href=\"http://www.hanzicraft.com/character/砥\">Stats</a> | <a href=\"https://www.google.com.au/search?q=砥&tbm=isch\">Google Images</a> | <a href=\"https://namakajiri.net/kanjigen/#砥\">Char lookup site</a></p>","glyphs":[{"glyph":"石","pinyins":["Shi2","dan4","shi2"]},{"glyph":"氐","pinyins":["di1","di3"]}]}